text: Michael James Moore (born August 21, 1970) is an American rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Philadelphia Category:Coxswains (rowing)
